This is a console application. Only cells from (0,0) to (200,50) are printed to the console. The executable is in ./Build/Products/Release.

Usage:

./GameOfLife /path/to/input.txt


./GameOfLife
Please provide a list of inputs (x,y), one live cell per line, then press crtl-d
(0, 1)
(1, 2)
(2, 0)
(2, 1)
(2, 2)
(-2000000000000, -2000000000000)
(-2000000000001, -2000000000001)

./GameOfLife
Please provide a list of inputs (x,y), one live cell per line, then press crtl-d

(last usage generates random board)